3日，7个政府军（其中有1名军官）、5名变节士兵以及3个平民在[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]交战中死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.newsmax.com/Newsfront/russia-syria-missiles/2011/12/01/id/419700 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2011-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111218182206/http://www.newsmax.com/Newsfront/russia-syria-missiles/2011/12/01/id/419700 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

4日，有至少12个来自一个情报机构的秘密警察变节，这似乎是巴沙尔核心圈的首次叛变。在[[伊德利卜|伊德利卜]]市中心的夜晚发生了由变节士兵攻击空军情报机构引发的枪战，双方有10人死伤<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/12/05/180867.html |title=-{Syria responds ‘positively’ to Arab League deal as it holds war games in show of force}- |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2012-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120228200913/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/12/05/180867.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在霍姆斯的激烈交战中有至少5名自由军死亡，1个受伤<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/11/us-syria-homs-idUSTRE7BA0JD20111211 |title=Bodies lie uncollected as Homs becomes war zone |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2011-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111213081032/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/11/us-syria-homs-idUSTRE7BA0JD20111211 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

5日，自由军在[[德拉省|德拉省]]的Dael打死4名政府军，其中包括一名军官<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sg.news.yahoo.com/34-syrians-seized-militia-found-dead-report-175118278.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2018-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105221214/https://sg.news.yahoo.com/34-syrians-seized-militia-found-dead-report-175118278.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

7日，双方士兵在伊德利卜的Saraqeb镇的广播中心附近激战，一辆政府军运输车被毁。同时，黄昏时分政府军在该镇的边缘地区的一个房屋内逮捕了3个活动家<ref>https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=139103779531302&id=121855461256134</ref>。

9日，一辆坦克在霍姆斯被毁<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2011/dec/09/syria-homs-massacre-warning-live-updates#block-5 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2011-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111213104718/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2011/dec/09/syria-homs-massacre-warning-live-updates#block-5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4个变节士兵死于战斗<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2011/dec/09/syria-homs-massacre-warning-live-updates#block-10 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2011-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111213104718/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2011/dec/09/syria-homs-massacre-warning-live-updates#block-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=333306023363207&set=a.221856221174855.74557.217848338242310&type=1</ref>。 

10日，安全部队攻击举行葬礼的人群，然后与自由军发生交火，有至少12人死亡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2011/12/10/syrian-forces-fire-on-funerals-battle-defectors/|agency=FOX News|date=2011-12-10|accessdate=2011-12-10|title=Syrian Forces Fire on Funerals, Battle Defectors|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181233/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2011/12/10/syrian-forces-fire-on-funerals-battle-defectors/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在西北部的Kfar Takharim镇有两辆军用运输车在燃烧<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/world/breakingnews/syrian-violence-kills-at-least-12-as-forces-fire-on-funeral-processions-clash-with-defectors-135374168.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2012-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305022014/http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/world/breakingnews/syrian-violence-kills-at-least-12-as-forces-fire-on-funeral-processions-clash-with-defectors-135374168.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

