自由军告诉记者，在霍姆斯一名[[准将|-{准}-将]]军官Salman al-Awaja由于拒绝向al-Quseir地区的民众开枪而于10日被处决，因此导致Salman领导的该军内部许多士兵发生叛变，随后变节士兵与效忠政府的士兵发生了冲突<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/syria-dec-12-2011-0931 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2012-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107024706/http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/syria-dec-12-2011-0931 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在Kfar Takharim的冲突中有2人死亡，2辆装甲车被毁<ref name="firstpost.com"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/syrian-military-vehicles-set-alight-as-violent-protests-spill-over-into-jordan-6275873.html |title=Syrian military vehicles set alight as violent protests spill over into Jordan |date=2011-12-12 |publisher=The Independent |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2011-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111214183956/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/syrian-military-vehicles-set-alight-as-violent-protests-spill-over-into-jordan-6275873.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

