===2012年===
==== 1月 ====
1月1日，在大马士革附近的Reef Damascus镇，政府軍为抓捕变节士兵，双方发生了交火<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.monstersandcritics.com/news/middleeast/news/article_1683458.php/Clashes-between-Syrian-army-and-defectors-says-opposition |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-12-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102131350/http://www.monstersandcritics.com/news/middleeast/news/article_1683458.php/Clashes-between-Syrian-army-and-defectors-says-opposition |archivedate=2012-01-02 }}</ref>。

8日，在[[德拉省|德拉省]]的Basr al-Hari镇，双方部队冲突导致许多人死亡，其中包括11名士兵<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/breaking-news/ci_19700338|title=Clashes kill 11 Syrian soldiers|agency=MercuryNews.com|date=2012-01-08|accessdate=2012-01-08|archive-date=2012-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314221743/http://www.mercurynews.com/breaking-news/ci_19700338|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

14日，叙人权观察报道，自由军与政府軍在霍姆斯的Hula地区交火<ref>http://www.africasia.com/services/news_mideast/article.php?ID=CNG.b55e62b1849467d932ccf3eb6b36cb49.441{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

1月中旬，自由军为了占领叙与黎巴嫩边界的Zabadani镇（属于[[大马士革省|大马士革省]]）与政府軍交战，该地距离大马士革仅14公里远。最终双方停火分别撤军。

1月26日，大马士革郊区Douma已经被反抗军控制，这些反抗军由武装的平民志愿者和变节军组成，主要使用[[步枪|步枪]]和[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-16771542 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-02-01 |archive-date=2012-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131204932/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-16771542 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由于有越来越多的政府军变节加入反对派，因此反對派也開始擁有坦克。自由军的发言人表示，1月28日有超过100名政府軍士兵变节，並带来了三辆坦克<ref name="In Rankous, Barely Holding On"/>。

29日到30日，超过2000名政府軍在超过50辆坦克的掩护下，进攻被反抗军控制的大马士革周边地区。到了30日夜晚，政府軍已经重新控制这些郊区，自由军则被迫撤退转移<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-16784711 |title=Syrian army returns to Damascus suburbs |accessdate=2012-02-01 |archive-date=2019-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422030919/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-16784711 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有10名自由军和8名政府军于30日战死，有2名变节士兵死于首都的Rankus郊区<ref name="thejakartaglobe.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/afp/syria-troops-crack-down-on-damascus-outskirts/494784 |title=Syria troops crack down on Damascus outskirts |access-date=2012-02-01 |archive-date=2013-01-04 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130104225447/http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/afp/syria-troops-crack-down-on-damascus-outskirts/494784 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另有报道说当天有19个平民和6个自由军死于郊区。而28日到30日这三天共计100人在这些地区死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/01/30/us-syria-idUSTRE80S08620120130 |title=Assad troops fight back against Syria rebels |accessdate=2012-02-01 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924162003/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/01/30/us-syria-idUSTRE80S08620120130 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。当天活动家报道，于2011年8月下旬被叙特种部队俘虏的自由军的创始人之一的陆军中尉Hussein Harmush，已经于前几周被当局[[处决|处决]]<ref name="thejakartaglobe.com"/>。

==== 2月 ====
2月1日，政府軍继续在大马士革周边行动。在首都西北方的Wadi Barada地区有14名自由军陣亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/02/01/world/meast/syria-unrest/?hpt=hp_bn2 |title=U.N. Security Council at standstill on Syria, reports of deaths rise |accessdate=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019231239/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/02/01/world/meast/syria-unrest/?hpt=hp_bn2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lccsyria.org/5962 |title=Syria Today 1-2-2012 |access-date=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2012-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120806202953/http://www.lccsyria.org/5962 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在Deir Kanoun和Ein al Fija镇也有冲突发生<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2012/feb/1/syrian-troops-move-new-rebel-areas-near-damascus/ |title=Syrian troops move on new rebel areas near Damascus |accessdate=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2014-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502084926/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2012/feb/1/syrian-troops-move-new-rebel-areas-near-damascus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[SANA|SANA]]报道，在德拉武装分子攻击一辆军用巴士造成1死2伤后，部队打死11名、打伤2名武装分子<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.cri.cn/6966/2012/02/01/2821s678712.htm |title=11 Gunmen Killed in Clashes with Syrian Gov't Troops |accessdate=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025184141/http://english.cri.cn/6966/2012/02/01/2821s678712.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Al-Watan报纸报道，各有27名和15名反抗军在霍姆斯和Rastan死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=2012%5C02%5C02%5Cstory_2-2-2012_pg7_10 |title=Deaths mount as Russia resists UN drive on Syria |accessdate=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2013-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227225227/http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=2012%5C02%5C02%5Cstory_2-2-2012_pg7_10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2月4日凌晨，自由军在霍姆斯袭击一个检查点打死10名政府軍士兵后，政府军对霍姆斯进行[[霍姆斯大轰炸|炮击和轰炸]]，造成至少200多平民死亡，1000多人受伤，许多房屋被毁<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/02/201223231333768854.html |title='Scores dead' in army assault on Syria's Homs |accessdate=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2018-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801025519/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/02/201223231333768854.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月5日，叙人权观察报道，在西北部的[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]和南部的[[德拉省|德拉省]]双方发生了交火，2个平民和9个士兵在伊德利卜死亡<ref name="AP-Lee-05-02-2012">{{cite web|url=http://hosted2.ap.org/APDEFAULT/3d281c11a96b4ad082fe88aa0db04305/Article_2012-02-05-ML-Syria/id-2d04856e03c14616a6756e5ebe98d5b0|title=After UN veto, US floats coalition on Syria|last=Matthew|first=Lee|coauthors=Bassem Mroue|date=Feb. 5, 2012 2:45 PM ET|publisher=Associated Press|language=en|accessdate=2012-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120827010909/http://hosted2.ap.org/APDEFAULT/3d281c11a96b4ad082fe88aa0db04305/Article_2012-02-05-ML-Syria/id-2d04856e03c14616a6756e5ebe98d5b0|archive-date=2012-08-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

自从2月13日开始，在霍姆斯省的Al-Qusayr双方发生了激烈交火。起初自由军占领了一处安全机构并打死了5人。其他政府軍士兵使用四辆坦克进攻反对派<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.monstersandcritics.com/middleeast/news/article_1690793.php/Death-a-daily-event-in-al-Qusayr-south-of-Homs |title=Death a daily event in al-Qusayr south of Homs |accessdate=2012-03-06 |archive-date=2012-07-20 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120720055240/http://news.monstersandcritics.com/middleeast/news/article_1690793.php/Death-a-daily-event-in-al-Qusayr-south-of-Homs |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过，其中一辆坦克和30个士兵变节投入反对派，后来自由军将其他政府军赶出该镇并控制了该地。他们表示在战斗中有20名政府军被打死，另外80个士兵逃跑。而自由军中有1人死亡、6人受伤<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/defectors-turn-the-tide-against-assad-forces/story-fnb64oi6-1226280989010 |title=Defectors turn the tide against Assad forces |accessdate=2012-03-06 |archive-date=2014-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328170936/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/defectors-turn-the-tide-against-assad-forces/story-fnb64oi6-1226280989010 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 3月 ====
3月1日，經過了27天的轟炸后，在缺乏弹药、水源和食物的条件下，自由军決定从Baba Amr地区「戰術性撤退」以確保居民安全，不过有4,000个居民拒绝离开该地区。政府軍隊順利進駐該地，而炮擊過程中有2名外國記者喪生<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/238846?tid=2 |title=27天炮轟擊退反對派‧敘利亞軍控制巴巴阿姆魯 |publisher=星洲日報 |date=2012年3月2日 |accessdate= }}</ref>。

3月3日，自由军宣布他们当天在大马士革郊区的游击战斗中打死了100多名政府军<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/32147-17-killed-in-syria-violence-as-syrian-free-army-kill-100-soldiers-in-reef-damascus |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-03-06 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128014054/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/32147-17-killed-in-syria-violence-as-syrian-free-army-kill-100-soldiers-in-reef-damascus |dead-url=no }}</ref>。当天在[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]，位于Abu Athuhoor军用机场的50个士兵准备乘坐飞机变节，不过被效忠政府的部队发现，其中47人被处决<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lccsyria.org/7087 |title=Syria Today 3-3-2012 |access-date=2012-03-06 |archive-date=2012-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120430190836/http://www.lccsyria.org/7087 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，只有3人成功逃跑。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/03/03/world/meast/syria-unrest/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |title=Dozens of defecting Syrian soldiers executed, activists say |accessdate=2012-03-06 |archive-date=2012-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622180926/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/03/03/world/meast/syria-unrest/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

3月11日，自由军与政府軍首次在首都[[大马士革|大马士革]]核心区Rukn Al-Din发生交火<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jpost.com/Headlines/Article.aspx?id=261395 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-03-13 |archive-date=2012-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109204833/http://www.jpost.com/Headlines/Article.aspx?id=261395 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 4月 ====
4月20日，国家电视台报道说在库奈特拉有10个政府軍士兵被反对派打死<ref>{{Cite news|title=Protests sweep Syria amid shaky truce as U.N. negotiates wider access for aid agencies|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-24|work=Al Arabiya|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/04/20/209069.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120422110125/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/04/20/209069.html|archivedate=2012年4月22日}}</ref>。

4月28日，在大马士革和拉塔基亚的冲突中，有数百名政府軍士兵变节加入反对派。9个政府軍士兵和反对派士兵在冲突中死亡。此外，反对派在拉塔基亚附近采用水陆两栖的方式攻击了政府軍<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/04/28/210874.html |title=Hundreds of Syrian troops defect near Damascus, Latakia, as clashes flare |publisher=English.alarabiya.net |date=2012-04-28 |accessdate=2012-05-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501090633/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/04/28/210874.html |archivedate=2012-05-01 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lccsyria.org/8208 |title=Syria Today 28-4-2012 | Local coordination committees of Syria |publisher=Lccsyria.org |date= |accessdate=2012-05-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120430193851/http://www.lccsyria.org/8208 |archivedate=2012-04-30 }}</ref>。

4月30日，20个政府军死于伊德利卜的三次连环爆炸<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/04/30/211156.html |title=At least 20 people killed in Idlib; top U.N. truce monitor takes over in Syria |publisher=English.alarabiya.net |date= |accessdate=2012-05-03 |archive-date=2017-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207064119/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/04/30/211156.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 5月 ====
5月2日，包括两名上校在内的15个政府軍士兵、2名反对派士兵，死于阿勒颇省的一次冲突<ref>{{cite web|title=مقتل 15 عنصرا نظاميا بينهم ضابطان في كمين في ريف حلب الشمالي|url=http://www.syriahr.com/2-5-2012-syrian%20observatory3.htm|publisher=Syrian Observatory for Human Rights|accessdate=2012-05-02|language=ar|archive-date=2012-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120514050637/http://www.syriahr.com/2-5-2012-syrian%20observatory3.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DT - 2 May 2012">{{cite news|title=Syria: 15 troops killed in Aleppo|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9240751/Syria-15-troops-killed-in-Aleppo.html|accessdate=2012-05-02|newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=2012-05-02|archive-date=2018-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181119045648/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9240751/Syria-15-troops-killed-in-Aleppo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Syria army suffers deadliest day since ceasefire|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9241244/Syria-army-suffers-deadliest-day-since-ceasefire.html|accessdate=2012-05-02|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|date=2012-05-02|archive-date=2018-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181119023635/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9241244/Syria-army-suffers-deadliest-day-since-ceasefire.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月14日，23个进攻[[Rastan|Rastan]]的政府軍士兵被自由军打死，之后政府軍猛烈袭击Rastan<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/05/201251413827733469.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archive-date=2018-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801034830/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/05/201251413827733469.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

5月20日，自由军在大马士革中部对政府軍发动广泛的袭击。Kafer Souseh、Mezzeh、Malki 和Ruk al Adn这几个地区都发生了密集的交火。自由军大马士革委员会宣布，Al Sahabeh营实施的一次军事行动成功暗杀了八名巴沙尔·阿萨德政府内政部与国防部的核心军官成员。叙内政部长Mohammed Shaar则否认有高官遭到暗杀，也否认在首都发生了猛烈的交火<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/may/20/syria-damascus-clashes-assassinations |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |archive-date=2012-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723223620/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/may/20/syria-damascus-clashes-assassinations |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lccsyria.org/8534 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005214912/http://www.lccsyria.org/8534 |archivedate=2015-10-05 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/05/20/215270.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |archive-date=2017-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010045412/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/05/20/215270.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。叙人权观察报道，复兴党伊德利卜地方分支领导人Adib Habb al-Rumman已被自由军暗杀。该组织也表示，自由军在最近的几周加大了对叙执政当局的长官与军官的暗杀力度<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.saidaonline.com/en/news.php?go=fullnews&newsid=37599 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |archive-date=2018-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118190917/http://www.saidaonline.com/en/news.php?go=fullnews&newsid=37599 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

5月21日，在政府軍进攻阿勒颇Atrarib的过程中，有至少11个自由军士兵和31个政府軍士兵死亡<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=399483 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120522054901/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=399483 |archivedate=2012-05-22 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lccsyria.org/8490 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005230208/http://www.lccsyria.org/8490 |archivedate=2015-10-05 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/syria-may-22-2012-0949 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |archive-date=2012-07-08 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120708091544/http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/syria-may-22-2012-0949 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 6月 ====
6月2日，有61名政府軍士兵在冲突中死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/06/20126382311504866.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-06-07 |archive-date=2012-06-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68deSQlM4?url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/06/20126382311504866.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月3日，至少80名政府軍士兵被反对派打死<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18325949 |title=Free Syrian Army rebels abandon Annan ceasefire |accessdate=2012-06-07 |archive-date=2012-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608003127/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18325949 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月7日，叙人权观察报道，24个政府軍士兵被自由军打死，其中包括一名在[[德拉|德拉]]被暗杀的[[上校|上校]]<ref name="syriahr.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archive-date=2016-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629163623/http://www.syriahr.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月8日，自由军与政府軍在中部[[大马士革|大马士革]]发生激烈交火。政府軍也继续炮轰中部霍姆斯<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/nation-world/ci_20813487/syrian-rebels-report-heavy-fighting-damascus-shelling-homs |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-06-10 |archive-date=2015-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008165118/http://www.mercurynews.com/nation-world/ci_20813487/syrian-rebels-report-heavy-fighting-damascus-shelling-homs |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dawn.com/2012/06/08/more-than-20-killed-in-syria-ngo/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-06-10 |archive-date=2012-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120610055718/http://dawn.com/2012/06/08/more-than-20-killed-in-syria-ngo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月9日，[[SANA|SANA]]报道，超过150名政府军、警察和执法人员在本周被反对派士兵打死。

6月9日，13个反对派士兵（其中10人死于霍姆斯省）和28个政府軍士兵死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://supportkurds.org/news/saturday-9-june-2012/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-06-15 |archive-date=2016-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406064110/http://supportkurds.org/news/saturday-9-june-2012/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月10日，至少16个政府軍士兵死亡<ref name="syriahr1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/11-6-2012-syrian%20observatory.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-06-15 |archive-date=2012-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718172214/http://www.syriahr.com/11-6-2012-syrian%20observatory.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自由军曾短暂地攻占了霍姆斯北部的al-Ghanto防空基地，并收获了大量的武器和弹药。后来该基地被政府軍武装直升机摧毁<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303410404577464763551149048.html?mod=googlenews_wsj |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-06-15 |archive-date=2012-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614204930/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303410404577464763551149048.html?mod=googlenews_wsj |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月11日，叙人权观察报道，有至少7个反对派士兵和23个政府軍士兵死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jun/12/syrian-forces-killing-children-un |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-06-15 |archive-date=2012-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120615201441/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jun/12/syrian-forces-killing-children-un |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

