6月21日，至少10个反对派被杀，其中5人死于德拉，一名变节指挥官死于伊德利卜<ref name="supportkurds.org">[http://supportkurds.org/news/thursday-21-june-2012/] {{Wayback|url=http://supportkurds.org/news/thursday-21-june-2012/ |date=20160405215329 }}. 21 June 2012. Syrian Observatory for Human Rights. Retrieved 23 June 2012.</ref>。54个政府执法人员在冲突中被杀<ref name="supportkurds.org"/>。

